    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular driving. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with no tears in the upholstery, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, shifts well, and all major systems are fully functional. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, ready-to-drive vehicle without the premium of a showroom-perfect example.",
