    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical work, as the engine runs roughly and there are visible fluid leaks under the chassis. The exterior shows substantial wear, including heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents across the body. The interior is also heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functioning electronic components. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a source for spare parts, but it is not currently recommended for daily use without major repairs.",
