      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape! It drives like a dream and is perfect for everything from daily commutes to fun weekend road trips. I've taken great care of it, and it's just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 28900.0,
