    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Power is transferred via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal traction through the apex. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. This is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated engineering, ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
