      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of performance and comfort. The exterior boasts a vibrant, original paint job that still holds a deep luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the smoke-free cabin feels fresh; the leather upholstery is in excellent shape with only minimal softening on the driver's side bolster. All interior tech, including the premium surround-sound system and navigation, is fully operational. Mechanically, this car is sound\u2014it has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. We recently replaced the tires and performed a full alignment, so it handles beautifully on the open road. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has many years of life left and is ready for a new owner who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect.",
